fields.title: Carrot
fields.description: Fresh carrots are crisp, vibrant, and naturally sweet with a bright orange hue. Their crunchy texture and earthy flavor make them perfect for eating raw or cooked. Packed with vitamins and antioxidants, carrots promote good vision and health. A versatile vegetable, they add color, nutrition, and freshness to every dish.

fields.title: Spinach
fields.description: Fresh spinach is tender, leafy, and vibrant green, offering a mild earthy taste with a hint of sweetness. Rich in iron, vitamins, and fiber, it supports strength and vitality. Whether eaten raw in salads, lightly saut√©ed, or blended into smoothies, spinach adds nutrition, freshness, and color to countless healthy dishes.

fields.title: Milk
fields.description: Fresh whole milk, rich and creamy with essential calcium and protein. Perfect for drinking, cooking, and baking, it supports strong bones and overall health.

fields.title: Cheddar Cheese
fields.description: Aged cheddar cheese with a sharp, tangy flavor and firm texture. Perfect for sandwiches, burgers, or grating over dishes.

fields.title: Bread Loaf
fields.description: Freshly baked bread loaf with a golden crust and soft, fluffy inside. Great for sandwiches, toasts, or serving with soups.

fields.title: Croissant
fields.description: Flaky, buttery croissant baked fresh daily. Perfect as a snack, breakfast pastry, or paired with coffee.
